No. 11-287. Skechers U.S.A., Inc., Petitioner v. Patty Tomlinson. 565 U.S. 1021, 132 S. Ct. 551,

181 L. Ed. 2d 410,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 8029. November 7, 2011.

Motion of Center for Class Action Fairness for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit denied.
